File:Eisanji sekitou.JPG|Nara – {{ill|Eizan-ji|de|Eizan-ji|ja|栄山寺}} stone seven‐tiered pagoda ({{ill|Kamakura Period|de|Kamakura-Zeit|ja|鎌倉時代}}, {{ill|Important Cultural Property|de|Wichtiges Kulturgut|ja|重要文化財}})
</gallery>

