File:讃岐国分寺 石造復元模型.JPG|{{ill|Sanuki Kokubunji|de|Sanuki Kokubunji|ja|讃岐国分寺|12=draft}} stone reconstruction model
File:Eisanji sekitou.JPG|Nara – {{ill|Eizan-ji|de|Eizan-ji|ja|栄山寺|12=draft}} stone seven‐tiered pagoda ({{ill|Kamakura Period|de|Kamakura-Zeit|ja|鎌倉時代|12=draft}}, {{ill|Important Cultural Property|de|Wichtiges Kulturgut|ja|重要文化財|12=draft}})
</gallery>

